                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Fiber can be equipped on Kubrows , Kavats , MOAs , and Hounds , but not on Sentinels ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Fiber",
                  "pageId": 511065,
                  "revisionId": 2696076,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Fiber cannot be equipped simultaneously with Metal Fiber ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Fiber",
                  "pageId": 511065,
                  "revisionId": 2696076,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Fiber uses the player's maximum Armor as the base, which means using Mods like Umbral Fiber ​ (with full set bonus), Armored Agility ​, Gladiator Aegis ​, Saxum Carapace , Jugulus Carapace , Carnis Carapace , Stand United (with Coaction Drift ) and Arcanes like Arcane Ultimatum , Arcane Guardian and Arcane Tanker can further increase a companion's maximum armor."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Fiber",
                  "pageId": 511065,
                  "revisionId": 2696076,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "With Link Fiber on any Beast companion, a maximum armor value of 4,694.26 (a 93.99% damage reduction) can be achieved using the above armor mods with Valkyr Prime ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Link Fiber",
                  "pageId": 511065,
                  "revisionId": 2696076,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "A companion can attain an even higher maximum armor value of over 5000 if the player chooses to use Chroma with a high power strength and the usage of Vex Armor . Exact numbers depend on accurate power strength, armor raising mods and Arcanes. With exactly 5000 armor, this would be a 94.34% damage reduction."
                }
              }
            ],
